code CSS sau để định dạng cho nút Hotline được đẹp lung linh hơn nhé!</p>\r\n<p>Copy toàn bộ đoạn code CSS dưới đây và dán vào sau thẻ đóng &lt;/body&gt; trong file <strong>footer.php</strong> của giao diện. (dán ngay bên trên đoạn code HTML vừa làm).</p>\r\n<div id=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926\" class=\"crayon-syntax crayon-theme-classic crayon-font-monaco crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate\" data-settings=\" minimize scroll-mouseover\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-plain-wrap\"> </div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-main\">\r\n<table class=\"crayon-table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"crayon-row\">\r\n<td class=\"crayon-nums \" data-settings=\"show\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-nums-content\">\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-1\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-2\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-3\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-4\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-5\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-6\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-7\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-8\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-9\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-10\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-11\">11</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-12\">12</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-13\">13</div>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-num crayon-striped-num\" data-line=\"crayon-5dce7e76858e2682072926-14\">14</div>\r\n<div